      def dist(p1, p2, dd=2):
      4
          ## approximate radius of earth in km
      5
          R = 6373.0
      6
          lat1 = radians(p1[1])
      7
          lon1 = radians(p1[0])
      8
          lat2 = radians(p2[1])
      9
          lon2 = radians(p2[0])
      10
      ​
      11
          dlon = lon2 - lon1
      12
          dlat = lat2 - lat1
      13
      ​
      14
          a = sin(dlat / 2)**2 + cos(lat1) * cos(lat2) * sin(dlon / 2)**2
      15
          c = dd * atan2(sqrt(a), sqrt(1 - a))
      16
      ​
      17
          return  R * c
